was still a young, aspiring lvl 10 mage, I was in a group in Northern Ro, attacking Derv camp 2. Tactics were discussed, to clear the camp of the 6-7 dervs in it. <br>
To my surprise, evryone agreed with the lvl 12 rogues' plan &quot;Caster first, all assist&quot;. Since I was the only caster in our team... <br>
Of course, everyone else had much more exp than I had, so shooting a firebolt into a fully packed Derv camp would probably have its uses. And, I must admit, I felt pretty honoured being the one to start the attack.<br>
So, silently, I waited until our rogue entered the camp, approached one of the spell-casting dervs,<br>
and shot.<br>
<br>
From there on, things didn't work out as planned. 1.3 seconds later, 6 dervs were on me. 0.5 second later, I was dead. 20 seconds later, the rest of the team was.  They lasted pretty long!<br>
I like tactics, really! I like to plan and perform a really &quot;neat&quot; kill. I'm just wondering if I'm very good at them... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=660066><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub22.ezboard.com/ualihjazanzibar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alihja Zanzibar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Her Wackyness</span><br>  Posts: 372<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(8/30/01 6:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub22.ezboard.com/frutabagaparadoxforumstupidcharactertricks.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=43.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.rutabaga-paradox.org/images/mullet.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Caster first!</span><hr size=1> Hehe!  Awesome story Etelka.  I remember doing something like that with my own magician.  I just think MOBS have the same strategy when there's a group of adcenturers approaching their camp.  <br>
